#about.modal.fade
    .modal-dialog
        .modal-content
            .modal-header
                %button.close{:data => {:dismiss => "modal"}} &times;
                %h4.modal-title About Tony
            .modal-body
                %p Hi there. My name is Tony Bruess.
                %p
                    I'm an 18 year old entrepreneur, thinker, and innovator. For my entire life I've had a passion for all things
                    %a{:href => "http://apple.com"} Apple
                    (hence the psuedonyms mrapple and MonsieurApple).
                %p
                    I'm also the co-founder and CEO of the
                    = succeed ',' do
                        %a{:href => "https://oc.tc"} Overcast Network
                    a Minecraft gaming service which provides software as a service to over 100,000 gamers every week.
                %p
                    Currently, I'm a first year student at
                    %a{:href => "http://stanford.edu"} Stanford University
                    with plans to study computer science and business.
                %p You can find me on the internet:
                %p#icons
                    - @media.each do |media|
                        %a{:href => media[:url], :target => "_blank"}
                            %i.fa.fa-2x{:class => media[:fa], :title => media[:title], :rel => "tt-top"}
